---
title: ShowMe — Behaviour Observer Flow
---
flowchart TD
    START([Launch ShowMe]) --> SESSION[Create timestamped session folder]
    SESSION --> READY{Ready — waiting for input}

    READY -->|Type text| TEXT[Log text note + auto-tag]
    READY -->|Click Screenshot| SCREEN[Capture full screen JPEG]
    READY -->|Click Voice| VOICE_START[Start mic recording]
    READY -->|Click Video| VIDEO[Record screen for N seconds]
    READY -->|Click System| SNAP[Capture processes, active window, CPU/RAM]
    READY -->|Click PSR| PSR_START[Start Windows Steps Recorder]

    TEXT --> CARD[Add timestamped card to timeline]
    SCREEN --> CARD
    VIDEO --> CARD
    SNAP --> CARD

    VOICE_START --> VOICE_REC{Recording...}
    VOICE_REC -->|Click Stop| VOICE_STOP[Save WAV file]
    VOICE_STOP --> CARD

    PSR_START --> PSR_RUN{PSR running...}
    PSR_RUN -->|Click PSR Stop| PSR_STOP[Stop PSR, save steps.zip]
    PSR_STOP --> CARD

    CARD --> LOG[Append event to timeline.jsonl]
    LOG --> READY

    READY -->|Close window| SHUTDOWN[Stop active recordings]
    SHUTDOWN --> SUMMARY[Generate session_summary.md]
    SUMMARY --> END([Session complete])

